longBusinessSummary: Flat Capital AB (publ) operates as an investment company that focuses on companies with various entrepreneurs worldwide. It holds investments in a portfolio of companies. Flat Capital AB (publ) was incorporated in 2013 and is based in Stockholm, Sweden.
